snippet.title: Heart Abyss - Official Reveal Trailer | Guerrilla Collective 2023 Showcase
snippet.description: Get a taste of the brutal, bloody action-platformer game Heart Abyss in this reveal trailer. Heart Abyss is set amidst the eternal war between humans and beastmen, and it is coming to PC.
